<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Error - Page Not Found</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .error-page {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .error-page h1 {
            font-size: 6rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FF6347; /* Tomato color */
        }
        .error-page p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
        .btn-home {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="error-page">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>Sorry! We can't seem to find the resource you're looking for.</p>
    <p>Please check that the Web site address is spelled correctly.<br>
    Or go to our home page, and use the menus to navigate to a specific section.</p>
    <a href="/user/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-home">Go to Home Page</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>